## mcp-proxy Configuration (CURRENT)

### ~/.claude.json (User Config)
Updated 2026-03-19 to include mcp-proxy under "D:/REPO/RUSTPROJECTS/MCP/mcp-proxy" project:

```json
"D:/REPO/RUSTPROJECTS/MCP/mcp-proxy": {
  "mcpServers": {
    "mcp-proxy": {
      "command": "D:/REPO/RUSTPROJECTS/MCP/mcp-proxy/target/release/mcp-proxy.exe",
      "args": ["--config", "mcp-servers.json"],
      "type": "stdio"
    }
  }
}
```

### Effect
- Claude Code CLI only sees **mcp-proxy** when in mcp-proxy project
- All downstream servers (gui-mcp, rules, rulestools) loaded via proxy's mcp-servers.json
- Issues MCP available via rulestools-mcp integration
- Crash recovery, graceful shutdown, and all Phase 5 features active

