## Verification

To verify mcp-proxy is configured:
1. In Claude Code, check that only "mcp-proxy" appears in available MCP servers
2. Proxy should load gui-mcp, rules, rulestools from mcp-servers.json
3. Check mcp-proxy.log for server initialization messages

```bash
tail -20 mcp-proxy.log
# Should show: "server loaded and initialized [server=gui-mcp]" etc
```
